Enjoy this split plan w/cathedral ceilings, lots of tile in living areas and gorgeous upgraded laminate wood like flooring in all bedrooms as well as in the  permitted enclosed florida room with a/c. Kitchen cabinets tastefully refurbished with pass through windows to florida room. Step outside from you large screened in pool area to pick your recently planted tangerine tree or tangerine-lime-lemon tree with timer sprinklers. Tax records show the interior to be 1,128sf and the enclosed additional 216sf fla. room creates a potential extended family room to this cutie!
